  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO ENACT INTO LAW THE INTERSTATE MASSAGE COMPACT AND PROVIDE THAT THE STATE OF MISSISSIPPI ENTERS THE COMPACT WITH OTHER STATES THAT JOIN IN THE COMPACT; TO AMEND SECTIONS 73-67-7,  73-67-15, 73-67-17, 73-67-19, 73-67-21, 73-67-27, 73-67-29 AND  73-67-31, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CONFORM TO THE PROVISIONS OF THIS ACT; TO AMEND SECTION 73-67-35, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CORRECT THE HOURS NEEDED FOR IN CERTAIN SUBJECT AREAS OF THE EDUCATIONAL REQUIREMENTS FOR MASSAGE THERAPY LICENSURE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
